{
  "texts": [
    "In the Attribute-Grained Preference Analysis Task, three random numbers of seeds-29, 33, 153, 42 and 757-were used in the experiment.",
    "For each experiment, we recorded the results and computed the mean and standard deviation of the evaluation metrics.",
    "These results are presented in Table 6.",
    "During the experiment, the weights and biases service (Weights & Biases software, wandb.com, CA, USA) was used to track all the different configurations of the parameters.",
    "The changes in the F1 measure on the validation set across training epochs for seeds 27, 42, and 757 are shown in Fig. 12."
  ]
}